Package com.swer348

Class Member

java.lang.Object
com.swer348.Member
Direct Known Subclasses:
Faculty, Staff, Student
public abstract class Member extends Object
The abstract class representing a member of an educational institution. It serves as the base class for specific member types like Students, Faculty, and Staff.
Since:
2023-11-19
Version:
